DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_009_c: You cannot hope to escape your fate.
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_010_b:
My power will sweep across this land.
You need but await the inevitable end.
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_012_b:
Was that the Demon King we were warned
about? It all really happened?!
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_013_b:
This is dire. The Demon King...the man
who nearly destroyed the world.
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_015_b: With his return, everyone's in danger.
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_016_b:
Oh, this isn't good! If that really was
him... Oh, we're in real trouble!
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_017_b:
Hold on... He must not be at his full
strength. Otherwise, why flee instead
of finishing us off?
DmT_BZ_GoBackBC_Text_018_b:
We should return to Lookout Landing and
decide what to do next.
